    <string name="menu_fastflageditor_title">FastFlag Editor</string>
    <string name="menu_fastflageditor_warning_text">FFlags (Fast Flags) are internal feature flags used by the Roblox client that can be changed remotely without requiring an update. They are intended only for Roblox engineers and staff and were not designed for regular users. While powerful, modifying FFlags is not recommended, as doing so can negatively affect how the Roblox client behaves or cause other unforeseen issues. Only use the editor to change FFlags if you are totally sure what you are doing with FFlags. Avoid importing large flag lists from others, whether created by people or generated by artificial intelligence (AI), that claim to improve performance or provide similar benefits. These can easily lead to serious issues. If you are doing this, stop immediately. \n\nDo you accept full responsibility for any consequences and still want to proceed?</string>

